|''Name''|html.CreateSafeURLEncoding|
|''Author''|[[Tobias Beer|http://tobibeer.tiddlyspace.com]]|
|''Description''|encodes a URL string into its failsafe version|
|''Source''|https://raw.github.com/tobibeer/TiddlyWikiPlugins/master/scripts/html.CreateSafeURLEncoding|
|''Version''|0.1 (2013-09-04)|
|''~CoreVersion''|2.5.2|
|''License''|Creative Commons 3.0|
<html>
<input style="display:block;min-width:600px" class="input" type=text value="[[Insert unsafe URL here]]"/>
<input style="display:block;min-width:600px" class="output" type=text value="encoded url will be inserted here"/>
<input style="display:block;min-width:606px;" type=button value="Generate safe link" onclick="
(function($,el){
  $(el).prevAll('.output')
      .val(
        encodeURIComponent(
          $(el).prevAll('.input').val()
        )
       ).focus().select();
})(jQuery,this);
return false;
"/>
</html>